<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Paige Hair Co.</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/square.ico">
    <link rel="preload" href="https://cdn3.editmysite.com/app/website/css/site.4b84f4c981da85f11ad4.css" as="style">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Work+Sans:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #d4a5a5;
            --secondary-color: #f0e1e1;
            --text-color: #5c3d3d;
            --highlight-color: #f7c7c7;
        }

        * {
            font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .loading-view {
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .loading-container {
            width: 62px;
            height: 54px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            grid-gap: 10px;
        }

        .dot-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: loading-view-movement 1.5s infinite;
        }

        .dot-container:nth-of-type(2) {
            animation-delay: 0.2s;
        }

        .dot-container:nth-of-type(3) {
            animation-delay: 0.4s;
        }

        @keyframes loading-view-movement {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .header a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s, text-decoration 0.3s;
        }

        .header a:hover {
            color: var(--highlight-color);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .about-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .about-section img {
            width: 320px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 2em;
            max-width: 500px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .instagram-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .instagram-section h2 {
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }

        .instagram-section a.button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .instagram-section a.button:hover {
            background-color: var(--highlight-color);
        }

        .location-hours-section {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .location-hours-section h3 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .location-hours-section p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .location-hours-section p span {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="loading-view">
        <div class="loading-container">
            <div class="dot-container"></div>
            <div class="dot-container"></div>
            <div class="dot-container"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Paige Hair Co.</h1>
        <a href="/services">Services</a>
        <a href="/book">Book</a>
        
    </div>
    <div class="about-section">
        <img src="pictures/aboutme.JPG" alt="About Me Picture of Paige">
        <p class="intro-text">
            Hi, I'm Paige! I'm a stylist at Rae Hair, and I am absolutely obsessed with what I do! Originally from
            Provo, UT, I've been in the hair industry for over 3 years, and I specialize in creating beautiful, lived-in
            colors, especially brunettes and blondes. Extensions are also one of my favorite things to work on!
            <br>
            <br>
            When I'm not behind the chair, you can usually find me at BYU sporting events or hanging out with my family,
            AND with my husband Jaykâ€”we've been married for over two years and couldn't be happier. We're both working
            hard toward our graduation in 2025!
            <br>
            <br>
            I absolutely love connecting with my clients and making them feel beautiful. I can't wait to have you in my
            chair soon! <br>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="instagram-section">
        <h2>Check out some of my work:</h2>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/paige.hairco/" class="button">Visit Instagram</a>
    </div>
    <div class="location-hours-section">
        <h3>Location & Hours</h3>
        <p><span>Rae Hair Salon</span></p>
        <p>4801 N. University Ave. #330 Suite 10<br>Provo, UT, 84604</p>
        <p><span> Hours:</span><br>
            Monday, Wednesday, Saturday: 10:00 am - 6:00 pm<br>
            Closed: Tuesday, Thursday, Friday, and Sunday
        </p>
    </div>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
            const loadingView = document.querySelector('.loading-view');
            loadingView.remove();
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>